- OVERVIEW
====================================================================
This script is an interactive CMD‑based installer and updater 
for Microsoft .NET components.

It supports installation of multiple versions of:

- .NET Runtime
- .NET SDK
- .NET Desktop Runtime
- ASP.NET Core Runtime
- Preview channels
- External installation scripts (PowerShell / Bash)

The tool uses winget, ANSI color output, 
and official Microsoft download sources.
====================================================================
2. ADMINISTRATOR PRIVILEGES
At startup, the script checks whether it is running 
with Administrator rights:

net session >nul 2>&1

If not, it automatically relaunches itself with elevated privileges:
Start-Process -FilePath "%0" -Verb RunAs
====================================================================
3. ENVIRONMENT SETUP
The script sets UTF‑8 encoding:

chcp 65001

This ensures proper rendering of ANSI colors and Unicode characters.
====================================================================
