====================================================================
5. INSTALLATION LOGIC
Each menu option triggers a corresponding winget installation, 
for example:

winget install Microsoft.DotNet.Runtime.7
winget install Microsoft.DotNet.SDK.8
winget install Microsoft.DotNet.DesktopRuntime.9
winget install Microsoft.DotNet.AspNetCore.6

Preview channels use:
Microsoft.DotNet.Runtime.Preview
Microsoft.DotNet.SDK.Preview
