7. ABOUT WINDOW
Option (b) displays a Windows Forms MessageBox with program information.
====================================================================
8. SCREEN HANDLING
Each installation step:

- Clears the screen
- Runs the installation
- Waits 3 seconds
- Returns to the main menu
====================================================================
9. EXIT
Option (x) exits the script.
